<pre class="lang-xml prettyprint-override"><code>&lt;data&gt;   &lt;nodeName type="attributeName"&gt;        VALUE1   &lt;/nodeName&gt;   &lt;nodeName type="attributeName2"&gt;         VALUE2   &lt;/nodeName&gt;   &lt;nodeName type="attributeName3"&gt;        VALUE3   &lt;/nodeName&gt; &lt;/data&gt; </code></pre>  <p>From this data, I have to check when 'attributeName' or 'attributeName2' exists, and do a bunch of front end display</p>  <pre class="lang-xml prettyprint-override"><code>&lt;div th:if="nodeName.type!=null &amp;&amp; nodeName.type['attributeName']"&gt;Do something &lt;/div&gt; &lt;span&gt; Non related display&lt;/span&gt; &lt;div th:if="nodeName.type!=null &amp;&amp; nodeName.type['attributeName']"&gt;Do something else&lt;/div&gt; </code></pre>